subject: The Devil in Miss Jones
sentence: The Devil in Miss Jones is a 1973 pornographic film, written, directed and produced by Gerard Damiano and starring Georgina Spelvin and Harry Reems.

subject: Basic Instinct
sentence: Basic Instinct is a 1992 neo-noir erotic thriller film directed by Paul Verhoeven and written by Joe Eszterhas.

subject: Zandalee
sentence: Zandalee is a 1991 American erotic thriller/romantic tragedy directed by Sam Pillsbury and starring Nicolas Cage, Judge Reinhold, Erika Anderson, Viveca Lindfors, Aaron Neville, Joe Pantoliano and Steve Buscemi.

subject: Triumph of the Will
sentence: Triumph of the Will (German: Triumph des Willens) is a 1935 Nazi propaganda film directed, produced, edited, and co-written by Leni Riefenstahl.

subject: Animals Are Beautiful People
sentence: Animals Are Beautiful People (also called Beautiful People) is a 1974 South African nature documentary written, produced, directed, filmed and edited by Jamie Uys, about the wildlife in Southern Africa, presented with comedic elements.

subject: Airport 1975
sentence: Airport 1975 (also known as Airport '75) is a 1974 American air disaster film and the first sequel to the successful 1970 film Airport.

subject: Where the Truth Lies
sentence: Where the Truth Lies is a 2005 British-Canadian erotic thriller film written and directed by Atom Egoyan and starring Kevin Bacon, Colin Firth, and Alison Lohman.

subject: Airline Disaster
sentence: Airline Disaster is an action disaster film directed by John J. Willis III and starring Meredith Baxter, Scott Valentine, Lindsey McKeon and Jay Beyers.

subject: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest
sentence: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest is a 2006 American fantasy swashbuckler film.
